step_data.thought: After clicking the 'Add to tree' button, I expected to see a modal or a dropdown where I can initiate the creation of a new directory. However, the page did not change after the click. This might be because the button's functionality is not implemented as expected or there might be a need to provide additional information such as the name of the new directory. Since the button did not lead to the intended action, I will check if there is a form or a dropdown that appears after clicking the button, and if not, I will attempt to provide the new directory name directly in the URL or in a different part of the UI.
